1.9.3 Release notes (2026-07-09)
=============================================================

### Changes

* Added optional styling overrides to `RingPublishingGDPRATTConfig` (`actionButtonCornerRadius`, `contentHorizontalMargin`, `descriptionFontSize`) for customizing the App Tracking Transparency explanation screen. All default to `nil`, so existing integrations render exactly as before.
* Added `contentAlignment` (`.topLeft` / `.center`) to `RingPublishingGDPRATTConfig`, controlling the layout of the logo and texts on the App Tracking Transparency explanation screen. Defaults to `.topLeft`, matching the previous layout.
